name: Cerebral Series I: PanicAttack
description: Cerebral Series I: PanicAttack Shortly after recovering from a panic attack myself, i came up with the concept for this piece and a concept to do something good with my art. I am donating 85% of the proceeds from the inital sales of all my NFTs to NAMI, the National Alliance on Mental Illness. You can read more about them here https://www.nami.org/About-NAMI/Donate-to-NAMI. Thanks for helping out and being a good human!
